Module edu.citadel.cprl
Package edu.citadel.cprl

Class Type

java.lang.Object
edu.citadel.cprl.Type
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayType, RecordType, StringType
public class Type extends Object
This class encapsulates the language types for the programming language CPRL. Type sizes are initialized to values appropriate for the CPRL virtual machine.

      public boolean isScalar()

    • typeOf

      public static Type typeOf(Token literal)
      Returns the type of a literal symbol. For example, if the symbol is an intLiteral, then Type.Integer is returned. Returns UNKNOWN if the symbol is not a valid literal symbol.
